
Introduction: 

helm install release-name  chart-name       -   deploy the kubernetes package.
helm upgrade release-name                   -   to update
helm uninstall release-name                 -   to delete 
helm rollback release-name                  -   to rollback objects.

helm verify                                 -   verify the package 
helm install --verify                       -   to verify before install.
helm package /chart -d destination/path     -   package the chart and place in destination path. 

